	<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 xl:py-32 bg-shadow">
		<div class="content-wrapper">
			<h3 class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance 2xl:text-7xl text-white">Exploring the Potential for Nature's Return</h3>
			<p class="mt-8 text-xl text-white">Inspired by the possibilities of rewilding? The next step is to consider whether it's the right approach for your specific piece of land and your goals. Rewilding isn't a one-size-fits-all solution, but its principles can be adapted to a wide variety of situations across Scotland.</p>
			<p class="mt-8 text-xl text-white">This page provides resources to help you think through the key considerations. We'll look at how to assess your land's potential, balance different objectives, and understand the practicalities involved. Remember, this is an information resource to guide your thinking; detailed assessments may require professional advice.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
