																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											'What is the land currently used for?',
																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											'Are there signs of degradation (e.g., soil erosion, lack of biodiversity)?',
																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											'What wildlife do you currently see?'
