			</div>

			<p class="mt-8 text-xl">Thinking through these questions doesn't provide a simple 'yes' or 'no' to rewilding, but it helps frame the possibilities and challenges. Your answers will guide you towards the most appropriate approaches and resources.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
