								<p class="text-lg mb-6">Focus could be on naturalising river channels, removing barriers to fish migration, creating or restoring ponds and wetlands, or establishing riparian buffer zones.</p>
								<a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary-dark font-medium">
									Read Wetland and River Restoration Guide
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
								</a>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="glide__slide">
							<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
								<h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Coastal Areas</h4>
								<p class="text-lg mb-6">Opportunities exist for saltmarsh and dune restoration, exploring seagrass or native oyster restoration (often requiring partnerships), and managing coastal habitats more naturally.</p>
